data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_12","content":"49:      font-family: var(--font-body);\n83:    .h1, h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h1); line-height: 1.04; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0; }\n84:    .h2, h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h2); line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.015em; margin: 0; }\n85:    .h3, h3 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h3); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.005em; margin: 0; }\n88:      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n95:    .meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-meta); color: var(--muted); }\n96:    .num  { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\n105:    .topnav .logo { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 19px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }\n155:      font-family: var(--font-display);\n166:      font-family: var(--font-display);\n174:      font-family: var(--font-display);\n186:      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n221:    .ds-table th { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }\n223:    .ds-table .num-col { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; text-align: right; }\n234:      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n338:    <section class=\"section hero\" data-od-id=\"hero\" id=\"top\">\n342:          <h1>Precision Roof Restore deserves a clearer roofing presence online.</h1>\n366:    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"services\" id=\"services\">\n370:          <h2>Give visitors the jobs they recognise, without making them hunt.</h2>\n377:            <h3>Roof restorations</h3>\n384:            <h3>Capping</h3>\n391:            <h3>Respray</h3>\n398:            <h3>Repairs</h3>\n405:            <h3>Gutters</h3>\n412:            <h3>Pressure cleaning</h3>\n419:    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"service-area\" id=\"areas\">\n423:          <h2>A Brisbane-first page that feels local without pretending to know every suburb.</h2>\n435:          <h3>“Tell us the roof type, suburb and the issue you are seeing.”</h3>\n441:    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"trust\">\n445:          <h2>Make the quote process feel straightforward.</h2>\n450:            <h3>Call or send the form</h3>\n455:            <h3>Describe the roof issue</h3>\n460:            <h3>Get a fast response</h3>\n465:            <h3>Move toward a quote</h3>\n472:    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"cta-strip\" id=\"enquiry\">\n476:          <h2>Call Precision Roof Restore now, or send the job details.</h2>\n","isError":false}

